Package com.juraj.hdbs.querying.language

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GlobalSQLListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by GlobalSQLParser.
    GlobalSQLVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by GlobalSQLParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GlobalSQLBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of GlobalSQLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    GlobalSQLBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of GlobalSQLVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
